author: NoiselessVolatileLobster
description: VibeCheck is a cog for counting good vibes and bad vibes for every user in the server. It is a very small facelift of Tobotimus' ReactKarma
install_msg: Thanks for installing `vibecheck`. See `[p]help VibeCheck` for details.
short: Good vibes? Bad vibes? You decide. Give them to other users and check the vibeboard to see how you're doing.
